com.lss233.phoenix.entity

接口 Entity

  • 所有超级接口:
    Identifiable, Locatable
    所有已知子接口:
    LivingEntity, Player

    public interface Entity
extends Locatable, Identifiable
    An entity is a Minecraft entity.

        Sets the vehicle entity(the entity that is ridden by this one).

        返回:
        True if the set was successful

      • getBaseVehicle

        Entity getBaseVehicle()
        Gets the entity vehicle that is the base of what ever stack the current entity is a part of. This can be the current entity, if it is not riding any vehicle. The returned entity can never ride another entity, that would make the ridden entity the base of the stack.
        返回:
        The vehicle entity, if available

        返回:

        返回:
